Test for NO_OP

Source: R/NO_OP.R

Test whether a given object is a NO_OP.

is_noop(x)

Arguments

x

any
Object to test.

Value

logical(1): Whether x is a NO_OP.

See also

Other Path Branching: NO_OP, filter_noop, mlr_pipeop_branch, mlr_pipeop_unbranch
